toolbox.name: Parcel Fabric
toolbox.summary: The Parcel Fabric toolbox contains tools that work with the internal feature classes and tables of a parcel fabric. Using the Parcel Fabric toolbox, you can migrate data to a parcel fabric, upgrade an existing parcel fabric, and create layer and table views on the parcel fabric.
